<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Anistorm</title>

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial;
  background: #0f0f0f;
  color: white;
}

header {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px;
  font-size: 28px;
  color: cyan;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
  gap: 15px;
  padding: 15px;
}

.card {
  background: #1a1a1a;
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 220px;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.card-content {
  padding: 10px;
}

.title {
  color: cyan;
  font-weight: bold;
}

button {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 8px;
  background: cyan;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
  background: #00cccc;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>🔥 Anistorm Anime Hub 🔥</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/289727.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">Demon Slayer</div>
<p>Tanjiro fights demons.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/36626.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">Attack on Titan</div>
<p>Humans vs Titans.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/3768124.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">Jujutsu Kaisen</div>
<p>Fight cursed spirits.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1118263.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">Naruto</div>
<p>Become Hokage.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1191374.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">One Piece</div>
<p>Find the treasure.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://wallpaperaccess.com/full/1398389.jpg">
<div class="card-content">
<div class="title">Death Note</div>
<p>Notebook of death.</p>
<button onclick="alert('Coming Soon')">Watch</button>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
